rComments: Hey kids, his last name is spelled "Rodgers"...

He is one of the better Italian teachers I have had. Way better than others. He is very concise on most questions and how he speaks. Best part was he would have natural and relevant conversations in Italian at the beginning of class which helps you learn more than just repetition. Overall, I would choose him as a professor for Italian
Daryl is awesome!  No other way about it.
daryl is amazing. and no he is not gay, actually married with one lovely child.
Awesome teacher, little work will get you an A, class is actually fun
